data.description: Nestled in the highly sought-after Lehi Crossing. Home features stunning mountain views, swimming pool, and large floorplan. All-new tile flooring throughout. Tandem garage was a workshop, w/ 50 amp 220 plug and dedicated 20 amp circuit. The heart of the home centers around the kitchen w/ample counter space. The adjacent family room with sliding glass doors, leads to a covered patio w/natural travertine. The massive master suite has a large walk in closet. Versatile loft space has the potential to be a fifth bedroom, home office, or playroom. The pool comes equipped with all the bells and whistles; includes a variable pump, baja step, and a cascade waterfall. Enjoy the community volleyball court or watch as children explore the numerous playgrounds throughout the community.
